Interface Queue<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements held in this queue
All Superinterfaces:
Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, Iterable<E>
All Known Subinterfaces:
Dequeue<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkedList, LinkedQueue
interface Queue<E> extends Collection<E>
A queue typically, but not necessarily, orders elements in a FIFO (first-in-first-out) manner.
